/-- If `f` is a function `‚Ñù ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ` satisfying `MemHS f` such that it is orthogonal
  to all `eigenfunction n` then the fourier transform of

  `f (x) * e ^ (- x ^ 2 / (2 Œæ^2))`

